cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.SD, cs.CE

This paper focuses on the influence of social networks on user behavior in a physical activity tracking application. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), cs.SD (Software Engineering), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
